  "markup": "Knee surgery is one of the most common and lucrative orthopedic surgeries, and sometimes it\u0026rsquo;s the best solution.  Before a knee case degrades into needing a surgical intervention, Super Pulsed Laser has a lot to offer both the acute and chronic knee pain patient, as well as ones that are rehabbing from their required surgery.\n\u003Cbr /\u003E\n\u003Cbr /\u003E\nJoin Dr. Chris Carraway and special guest as they discuss Knee Conditions and ways Super Pulsed Laser can help these patients."
}]]></Value>
